<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Email Tesdiqi – Seafarer</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #05131f;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #e8e0d4;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #05131f;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0a1e30 0%, #021527 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.25);
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* ── Header ── */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #021527 0%, #0d2a40 100%);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c9a96e;
            padding: 38px 48px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header .anchor-icon {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
            color: #c9a96e;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 0 4px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .header p.tagline {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #c9a96e;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* ── Body ── */
        .body {
            padding: 48px 48px 40px;
        }

        .body h2 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #c9a96e;
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 50px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c9a96e, transparent);
            margin: 0 0 28px;
        }

        .body p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #cfc8be;
            margin: 0 0 16px;
        }

        .body p strong {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* ── Button ── */
        .btn-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 36px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 44px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a8885a);
            color: #021527 !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.06);
            border-left: 3px solid #c9a96e;
            border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 28px 0 0;
        }

        .info-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #a09688;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        .footer {
            background-color: #021020;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.15);
            padding: 28px 48px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #5a6070;
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer .brand {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #c9a96e;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">

            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="header">
                <span class="anchor-icon">⚓</span>
                <h1>Seafarer</h1>
                <p class="tagline">Yacht &amp; Boat Rental</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Body -->
            <div class="body">
                <h2>Email Tesdiqi</h2>
                <div class="divider"></div>

                <p>Salam, <strong>{{FullName}}</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Seafarer ailəsinə xoş gəlmisiniz! Qeydiyyatınızı tamamlamaq üçün
                    aşağıdakı düyməyə klikləyin və email ünvanınızı təsdiq edin.
                </p>

                <div class="btn-wrapper">
                    <a href="{{ConfirmUrl}}" class="btn">&#9654;&nbsp; Emaili Tesdiq Et</a>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <p>
                        ⚠️ Bu link <strong>24 saat</strong> ərzində etibarlıdır.
                        Əgər bu hesabı siz yaratmamısınızsa, bu emaili nəzərə almayın.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Bu email avtomatik göndərilmişdir, cavab verməyin.</p>
                <p>© 2025 Seafarer. Bütün hüquqlar qorunur.</p>
                <div class="brand">⚓ Seafarer</div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
